6. How we Protect personal information
 Under the premise of ensuring the accuracy and completeness of your personal data, we implement a series of physical, technical and management measures to protect your personal data from unauthorized access, disclosure, use, modification, damage or loss. For example:
(1) We encrypt your personal information when storing or transmitting them over the network;
(2) Our employees who have access to personal information have signed confidentiality agreements and we will regularly conduct training to ensure that they understand and comply with these agreements;
(3) We have strict access control procedures to limit access to your personal information to only those employees or agents who need to know this information in order to provide you with the service you have requested.

